entries.femaleVariant: It isn't right! It's like they forgot people live here!
They think AVs don't make noise? I can barely sleep.
Ugh, same here. The kids're still out like a light, but I can barely stand it. Must have to do with age.
I went to the council to file a complaint. You know what they said?
"If it bothers you so much, go get some cochlear plugs."
My windows rattle when they fly by. Wonder if they'll think up an implant for that!
